# RentAll Repo Routing

Use these repo roots by request type:

- UI work: `C:/RentAll/RentAll.Ui`
- API work: `C:/RentAll/RentAll.Api`
- DB work: `C:/RentAll/RentAll.Db`

When the user asks a UI question, work in the UI repo by default.
When the user asks an API question, work in the API repo by default.
When the user asks a DB question, work in the DB repo by default.

If the request is ambiguous or cross-cutting, ask one clarifying question before editing.
